STATE of North Carolina
v.
Dwight PARKER, Sr. No. 306P04-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 25, 2007. Dwight Parker, Sr., Pro Se. Kathleen U. Baldwin, Assistant Attorney General, Clark Everett, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 2nd day of November 2006 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Pitt County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 25th day of January 2007."
